\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 develops around the fireball. 
\par }{\b\f0\fs22\cf1\insrsid15550680 
\par }{\b\f0\fs22\cf1\insrsid3347702\charrsid14289276 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 \hich\f0 - 6 seconds after the explosion\'85}{\f0\fs22\cf1\insrsid3347702\charrsid14289276 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  
